#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linspace.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linspace"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:1 of
msgid "Return evenly spaced numbers over a specified interval."
msgstr "在指定区间内返回均匀间隔的数字。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns `num` evenly spaced samples, calculated over the interval "
"[`start`, `stop`]."
msgstr "返回在区间 [`start`, `stop`] 上计算出的 `num` 个均匀间隔的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:6 of
msgid "The endpoint of the interval can optionally be excluded."
msgstr "区间的端点可以选择性地被排除。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:8 of
msgid "The starting value of the sequence."
msgstr "序列的起始值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:10 of
msgid ""
"The end value of the sequence, unless `endpoint` is set to False. In that"
" case, the sequence consists of all but the last of ``num + 1`` evenly "
"spaced samples, so that `stop` is excluded.  Note that the step size "
"changes when `endpoint` is False."
msgstr ""
"序列的结束值，除非 `endpoint` 设置为 False。在这种情况下，序列包含 ``num "
"+ 1`` 个均匀间隔样本中除了最后一个的所有样本，因此 `stop` 被排除。注意当 "
"`endpoint` 为 False 时，步长会发生变化。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:15 of
msgid "Number of samples to generate. Default is 50. Must be non-negative."
msgstr "要生成的样本数量。默认为 50。必须为非负数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:17 of
msgid ""
"If True, `stop` is the last sample. Otherwise, it is not included. "
"Default is True."
msgstr "如果为 True，`stop` 是最后一个样本。否则，它不被包含。默认为 True。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:20 of
msgid ""
"If True, return (`samples`, `step`), where `step` is the spacing between "
"samples."
msgstr "如果为 True，返回 (`samples`, `step`)，其中 `step` 是样本之间的间隔。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:23 of
msgid ""
"The type of the output tensor.  If `dtype` is not given, infer the data "
"type from the other input arguments."
msgstr "输出张量的类型。如果未提供 `dtype`，则从其他输入参数推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:26 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:28 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:31 of
msgid ""
"* **samples** (*Tensor*) -- There are `num` equally spaced samples in the"
" closed interval   ``[start, stop]`` or the half-open interval ``[start, "
"stop)``   (depending on whether `endpoint` is True or False). * **step** "
"(*float, optional*) -- Only returned if `retstep` is True    Size of "
"spacing between samples."
msgstr ""
"* **samples** (*Tensor*) -- 在闭区间 ``[start, stop]`` 或半开区间 ``["
"start, stop)`` 中有 `num` 个等间距的样本（取决于 `endpoint` 是否为 True）"
"。* **step** (*float, 可选*) -- 仅当 `retstep` 为 True 时返回，表示样本"
"之间的间距大小。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:31 of
msgid ""
"**samples** (*Tensor*) -- There are `num` equally spaced samples in the "
"closed interval ``[start, stop]`` or the half-open interval ``[start, "
"stop)`` (depending on whether `endpoint` is True or False)."
msgstr ""
"**samples** (*Tensor*) -- 在闭区间 ``[start, stop]`` 或半开区间 ``[start,"
" stop)`` 中有 `num` 个等间距的样本（取决于 `endpoint` 是否为 True）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:34 of
msgid "**step** (*float, optional*) -- Only returned if `retstep` is True"
msgstr "**step** (*float, 可选*) -- 仅当 `retstep` 为 True 时返回"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:36 of
msgid "Size of spacing between samples."
msgstr "样本之间的间距大小。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`arange`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:41 of
msgid ""
"Similar to `linspace`, but uses a step size (instead of the number of "
"samples)."
msgstr "与 `linspace` 类似，但使用步长（而不是样本数量）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`logspace`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.linspace.linspace:44 of
msgid "Samples uniformly distributed in log space."
msgstr "在对数空间中均匀分布的样本。"

